flowchart TD
    A[input] --> B{entry path}
    B -->|situation.md| C[adc complain\nload linked files\ndraft complaint.md]
    B -->|complaint.md| D[adc case\nload complaint and linked files]
    B -->|scenario.json| E[load formal scenario]

    C --> D
    D --> F[case generation\npacket, strategies,\ncase_init]
    F --> G[build formal scenario]
    E --> G

    G --> H{case_init present?}
    H -- yes --> I[Lean initialize_case]
    H -- no --> J[authoritative CourtState]
    I --> J

    J --> K[Lean next_opportunity]
    K --> L{terminal?}
    L -- yes --> W[write artifacts\nrun db, events,\ntranscript, digest]
    L -- no --> M[Lean role_view]
    M --> N[runner prompt assembly\nrole preamble,\nvisible case,\ntool cards]
    N --> O{local role or ACP role}
    O -->|local| P[local model call]
    O -->|ACP| Q[ACP session\n_adc methods plus\none ephemeral home]
    P --> R[proposed decision or pass]
    Q --> R
    R --> S[Lean apply_decision]
    S --> T{valid?}
    T -- no --> U[correction message\nsame opportunity]
    U --> O
    T -- yes --> V[execute accepted act\nLean step or\nrunner action]
    V --> J
